&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
This is a problem because non-admin users will be shown a warning that they're not authorised to view the package if they click on the link.
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
At CKAN.net currently, this affects the most recent comment.
&lt;/p&gt;
